# 🚀 Demo Project

A simple and clean demo project built to understand the basics of web development using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript / React**.

---

## 📌 Overview

This project is created as a beginner-friendly demo to:

- Understand project structure
- Learn basic frontend development
- Practice Git & GitHub workflow
- Build and run a simple web application

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- 🌐 HTML5
- 🎨 CSS3
- ⚡ JavaScript  
- ⚛️ React (if applicable)

